re points a touchdown is worth. Touchdowns can be worth a maximum of 7 points. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a pass clock. Hold onto the ball too long and it will explode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/708720/extras/9b7360fc3d740c0a0f3c29b577451687.poster.avif?t=1773932684\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/708720/extras/9b7360fc3d740c0a0f3c29b577451687.webm?t=1773932684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/708720/extras/9b7360fc3d740c0a0f3c29b577451687.mp4?t=1773932684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
